### 게시글 생성
POST /localhost:8080/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "title",
    "content": "content",
    "createdBy": "createdBy",
    "tags": ["tag1", "tag2"]
}

### 게시글 수정
PUT  /localhost:8080/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "title",
    "content": "content",
    "updatedBy": "haeni",
    "tags": ["tag1", "tag2"]
}

### 게시글 삭제
DELETE /localhost:8080/posts/1?createdBy=haeni

### 게시글 상세조회
GET /localhost:8080/posts/1

### 게시글 목록조회
GET localhost:8080/posts?page=0&size=10&tag=kotlin
